  "original_title": "Pfizer vaccination centres at CMC today",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Pfizer vaccination centres at CMC today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Colombo Regional Epidemiologist Dr. Dinu Guruge today requested those who are over 20 years of age to get the COVID-19 vaccine dose against the virus from the CMC Vaccination Centres today.",
        "She said the people who are eligible to get the vaccine should be over 20 years of age and should have completed three months since their last COVID jab.",
        "The people are advised to visit the MOH Office at Ginthupitiya, MCH and MOH office at Deans Road, New Bazaar Maternity Home, MOH office at Wellawatte, Campbell Park and MOH Office at Kirula Road to get their first, second, third and fourth Pfizer COVID-19 vaccine doses from 9:00 am to 1:00 pm today.",
        "However, the health ministry said the fourth dose is recommended for people between 20 and 60 years of age and for those with immunodeficiency and chronic disorders. (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)"
      ],
